messages.messageBody:
In a message dated 6/15/03 6:42:44 PM, julie@... writes:

<< > INFP: I Never Find Perfection >>

The Rolling Stones have a song about that!

The other day I was in the car and heard part of a song, and I'm not sure
what it was!
Maybe someone here will recognize it.

It sounded like the guitar parts of the Beatles "Day Tripper," but it sounded
more solidly like the Rolling Stones' "Satisfaction," and maybe it was
building up to be neither. Anyone know who or what that was?

Sandra
